
Kubernetes Architecture working

A Kubernetes master runs Control Plane responsible for maintaining the desired state of the cluster.
K8s having 5 components in a kubernetes master cluster
-
Etcd	- This is a data store used by Kubernetes to store all information about the cluster.
kube-apiserver	- This component exposes Kubernetes API to users allowing them to create API resources, run applications
kube-controller-manager	- The component that manages API  created by users. It makes sure that the actual state of the cluster always matches the desired state
kube-scheduler	- This component is responsible for scheduling user workloads. When scheduling applications, kube-scheduler considers various factors such as available node resources, node health, and availability.
cloud-controller-manager	- The component that manages API  which interact with the cloud providersâ€™ APIs.
